text: Paulina Sarkanaitė (born 16 August 1998) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a defender for Gintra Universitetas and the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
